name: CC0394 - ITP-013 - Fencing and Acoustic Wall Construction REV01
Template Name: CC0394 - ITP-013 - Fencing and Acoustic Wall Construction REV01

name: Ensure that the following items have been actioned: SWMS if applicable; Plant Pre-start Inspection; Service locations identified; Traffic Management Plans (if required); All staff inducted

Acceptance criteria - SWMS submitted reviewed and accepted if required. Plant inspections completed and entered. Pre-work briefings completed. Service Diagrams available and services located. Has all of the above been completed?
Verification of acceptance by Symal - Key - H
Have any/all of the above permits been acquired/completed and signed off?
Freq - Prior to start of works
Verification of acceptance by Symal - Key - H
Acceptance criteria - Fencing or acoustic wall Material complies with specifications and IFC Drawings. Do the construction materials comply with regulations and drawings?
3600mm Acoustic wall post & panel (including 1200mm retaining wall)
Freq - Prior to start of works
Verification of acceptance by Symal - Key - H

Acceptance criteria - All logs, stumps, saplings, and undergrowth within 1 m of the fence line, and all trees which will interfere with the proper construction of the fence shall be removed and disposed of safely and correctly. High points shall be cut down to provide the clearance shown on IFC drawings and low spots shall be filled with surplus earth from holes and trimmings. Has all of the above been completed safely and correctly to IFC drawings?
Verification of acceptance by Symal - Key - I

Acceptance criteria - Surveyor to set fencing alignment and individual post/sleeve set out in accordance with IFC alignment plan/design model. Has all of the above been completed safely and correctly to IFC drawings?
Verification of acceptance by Symal - Key - I
Acceptance criteria - Physically check survey set out of fencing alignment. Has the above been completed complies to IFC drawings ?
Verification of acceptance by Symal - Key - I
Acceptance criteria - Has the footing location and height been set out by a Surveyor?
Verification of acceptance by Symal - Key - S
Acceptance criteria - Hole to be excavated to the depth and diameter specified in the design drawings. The design dimensions are:
Verification of acceptance by Symal - Key - S
Acceptance criteria - Is the hole clean and free of debris & water?
Verification of acceptance by Symal - Key - H
Acceptance criteria - Confirm concrete grade is 25 Mpa [KN3] or better.
Verification of acceptance by Symal - Key - H
Acceptance criteria - The fence post will be inserted into the footing and measured for verticality with spirit level. Has all of the above been completed safely and correctly?
Verification of acceptance by Symal - Key - I
Acceptance criteria - Has concrete been allowed to cure for at least 24hrs prior to proceeding?
Verification of acceptance by Symal - Key - H
4.2 - Installation of tension Wires and Bracing

Acceptance criteria - Once post have been installed, tension wire is to be installed as per IFC drawing. CHS Brace to be installed at the end bays and Corners fixed at each end via approved proprietary post and rail clamps. Has all of the above been completed safely and correctly?
Verification of acceptance by Symal - Key - I

Acceptance criteria - Chain mesh to be installed as per IFC Drawing. Chain wire mesh shall be tightened and securely fastened to posts and spaced at not more than 400 mm intervals online posts and at not more than 500 mm intervals online wires. Has all of the above been completed safely and correctly?
Verification of acceptance by Symal - Key - I
4.4 - Installation of acoustic and retaining wall panels
Acceptance criteria - Panels have been installed so that the faces between panels are flush at the joints. Panels have been checked for verticality using a spirit level.
Verification of acceptance by Symal - Key - I

Acceptance criteria - Install gates of the type, size and location as specified on IFC Drawings. Gate posts are to be of the dimensions and firmly set in the ground to the depth specified on IFC drawings. All gates shall be hung with galvanized hinges securely attached to gate posts and be able to swing freely. Has all of the above been completed safely and correctly?
Verification of acceptance by Symal - Key - I
Acceptance criteria - Have earth tabs been welded to the fence at every third post?
Acceptance criteria - Has soil behind the retaining wall been compacted as per the IFC drawings:

Acceptance criteria - Unless stated otherwise, tolerances for the construction of fencing shall be as follows: (a) the vertical tolerance on the height of fencing shall be ± 20 mm from the design line. (b) the longitudinal line tolerance for fencing shall be ± 20 mm in plan view; and (c) the tolerance on the verticality of fencing shall be 1 in 50. Has all of the above been completed safely and correctly?
Verification of acceptance by Symal - Key - I
Remarks/record - Third Party Compliance of installed fencing
Acceptance criteria - Have ‘Danger, High voltage, authorised personnel only’ signs been attached to the fence?
Verification of acceptance by Symal - Key - I
5.1[KN5] - Quality Representative to check the above criteria and records to confirm
Acceptance criteria - All above criteria met, and records identified attached.
Verification of acceptance by Symal - Key - R
Completed Checklist (if applicable) and reports and other compliance records attached.
Acceptance criteria - As-built survey of work lot attached. All points within tolerance.
Verification of acceptance by Symal - Key - H
